<section class="mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-white/10">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight uppercase">Barbershop FAQ</h2>
  <div class="space-y-5">
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">1) How often should I get a haircut?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Most clients come every 2–4 weeks depending on style, growth rate, and how clean they want their fade or taper to stay.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">2) Do you take walk-ins or appointments only?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Both. Walk-ins are welcome when chairs are open, but appointments are the best way to lock in your time.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">3) What should I ask for if I don’t know haircut names?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Bring 1–2 reference photos and explain your routine. Your barber can recommend the right cut for your head shape and lifestyle.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">4) How long does a fade appointment take?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Most fade services take around 35–60 minutes depending on hair density, beard work, and detailing.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">5) Do you do beard trims and lineups?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Yes. Beard shaping, lineup cleanup, and full beard sculpting are available as add-ons or standalone services.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">6) How do I keep my haircut fresh between visits?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Use quality shampoo/conditioner, brush daily, keep your neckline maintained, and rebook before your shape fully grows out.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">7) Can I book for kids’ cuts too?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Absolutely. Kid-friendly cuts are available with styles adjusted for age, activity, and school standards.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">8) What areas do you serve around Manor?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">We regularly serve Manor, Pflugerville, East Austin, Elgin, and nearby communities.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">9) What’s the best haircut for hot Texas weather?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Mid/low fades, textured crops, and lightweight beard shaping tend to stay cleaner and cooler in Central Texas heat.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">10) Where can I book an appointment?</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">Book online at <a href="https://app.thecut.co/barbers/thelab" class="underline">The Lab on The Cut</a> or call 512-305-3335.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
